NL Question: What is the name of the party that Legislator Al Green, whose lastName is 'Green', is a member of?
Cypher: MATCH (l:Legislator {lastName: 'Green', firstName': 'Al'})-[:IS_MEMBER_OF]->(p:Party) RETURN p.name AS partyName;

NL Question: What is the state code that Legislator David McKinley, whose lastName is 'McKinley', represents?
Cypher: MATCH (l:Legislator {lastName: 'McKinley', firstName': 'David'})-[:REPRESENTS]->(s:State) RETURN s.code AS stateCode;

NL Question: What is the URL of the committee that Legislator Marco Rubio, whose lastName is 'Rubio', serves on, where his rank is 3?
Cypher: MATCH (l:Legislator {lastName: 'Rubio', firstName': 'Marco'})-[r:SERVES_ON {rank: 3}]->(c:Committee) RETURN c.url AS committeeURL;

NL Question: What is the type of body that legislator Harold Rogers was elected to?
Cypher: MATCH (l:Legislator {firstName: 'Harold', lastName': 'Rogers'})-[:ELECTED_TO]->(b:Body) RETURN b.type AS bodyType;

NL Question: What is the title of the bill that Bruce Westerman voted on?
Cypher: MATCH (l:Legislator {firstName: 'Bruce', lastName': 'Westerman'})-[:VOTED_ON]->(b:Bill) RETURN b.officialTitle AS billTitle;

NL Question: What is the name of the committee to which Elizabeth Warren has the rank 12?
Cypher: MATCH (l:Legislator {firstName: 'Elizabeth', lastName': 'Warren'})-[r:SERVES_ON {rank: 12}]->(c:Committee) RETURN c.name AS committeeName;
